title: OpenSSL 0.9.8h for Windows
description:
For programs that use OpenSSL like Second Life and quite a few email clients. The usual source for Windows users is Shining Light Productions, but their latest offering didn\\\&#039;t work (for me at least). Since up-to-date binary builds on Windows are hard to find, this will hopefully save a few people a bit of trouble. 

These are the two dll\\\&#039;s that most people will want, and are taken from the latest win32 build of Apache HTTP Server. 

libeay32.dll
